Job Description
Pricing of all kinds of leather to customers after consultation with Director. Correspondence with customers & agents about Order booking, Shipment information, Order status & Leather complains. To maintain complete record of leather contracts regarding color, quantity, thickness mode of shipment, destination or specific remarks pertaining to goods. Liaison with factory regarding delivery dates of orders, leather complains & samples. Follow up of export overdue payments with customers Follow up with concern customers & agents to provide invitation letters for director to visit abroad and also arrangement of invitation & chamber recommendation letters for customer to visit our tannery in Pakistan. Proficiency in English communication (both verbal and written). Candidates having experience to work in Export Department at comparative level in manufacturing concern would be preferred.
Job Specification
Proficiency in English communication (both verbal and written).Team Player having Leadership skills.Emotional stability.Outspoken, god negotiation skills.Proficiency in MS Office
